data.description: Beautiful, move in ready, 2 bed 2 bath in the adult community of Springfield!  20% of homeowers can be 40+. This home has been meticulously maintained.  Kitchen is updated to include white cabinets, granite countertops and black appliances.  Large Master bedroom with spacious walk in closet off of the bath.  Second bedroom has Murphy bed and built in desk making it a great space for guests and an office.  Oversized laundry with cabinets for extra storage.  Extended garage complete with built in Storage and work bench.  HVAC system replaced in 2020. Exterior recently painted.  Community has a restaurant, golf course, two pools, a hot tub, tennis and pickleball courts, fitness center, activity rooms and more!
